verbose_text: Serum levels of tumor necrosis factor alpha, interleukin-6, intercellular cell adhesion molecule-1 and vascular endothelial growth factor were detected using an enzyme linked immuno-sorbent assay; the reductase method was performed to detect serum nitric oxide levels.
